  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Champion Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Cleric Order</span></strong></span></p><p>You gain 1 additional Divine Domain.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Divine Blessing</span></strong></span></p><p>When you use Divine Blessing you can spend additional MP to enhance the effect:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Destruction</strong>: The damage increased by 2 per MP spent.</p></li><li><p><strong>Restoration:</strong> The healing increases by 2 per MP spent.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Channel Divinity</span></strong></span></p><ul><li><p><strong>Divine Rebuke:</strong> The damage increases by 1.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lesser Divine Intervention:</strong> The pool of HP increases by 2.</p></li></ul>",
